         <div xml:lang="grc" type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><ab>
    <lb n="1"/>Ἀπολλώνιος Χαιρήμονι τῶι 

    <lb n="2"/>γυμνασιάρχωι χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>Σ<unclear>ωχ</unclear>ώτης χρησάμενος ἐν τῆι <expan>πόλ<ex>ει</ex></expan>, 

    <lb n="4"/>θέλων <choice><reg>ἀποδοῦναι</reg><orig>ἀποδο͂ναι</orig></choice> τὰς ἑκατὸν <num value="100"/> δρα

    <lb n="5" break="no"/>χμὰς, οὐχ εὗρέ σε, τοῦ δὲ σὲ <choice><reg>μὴ</reg><orig>μὴι</orig></choice> εὑ

    <lb n="6" break="no"/>ρεθῆναι ἀποδέδωκε αὐτὰς <choice><reg>ἄνω

    <lb n="7" break="no"/>θεν</reg><orig>ἄνω<lb n="7" break="no"/>θον</orig></choice>, <choice><reg>ἵνα</reg><orig>εἵνα</orig></choice> φιλάνθρωπον εἰς δύο <num value="2"/> 

    <lb n="8"/>τόπους <choice><reg>μὴ</reg><orig>μὴι</orig></choice> χορηγῆι. <app type="editorial"><lem resp="bgu 2 p.357">Θε<unclear>ωνε</unclear>ία<unclear>ς</unclear></lem><rdg>Θέ<unclear>ων</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/></rdg></app> δὲ 

    <lb n="9"/>ἔγραψέ μοι ἐπιστολὴν ὅτι ἔλεγας 

    <lb n="10"/>ὅ<supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear>ι</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>α<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> ἐ</supplied>στιν ἐλαιὼν τὸν χ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><abbr><unclear>ν</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/></abbr> 

    <lb n="11"/>οὐ μό<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied>ον <app type="editorial"><lem resp="bgu 2 p.358">δὲ αὐ<supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear>ὸ</unclear>ς</lem><rdg><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/>υ<supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear>οσ</unclear></rdg></app> ἔγραψε <unclear>ἀ</unclear>λλὰ 

    <lb n="12"/>καὶ Ἀμμωνᾶτος καὶ Πασίωνος κατα

    <lb n="13" break="no"/>βάντων <add place="above">ε<unclear>ἰς</unclear></add> τὸ αὐτὸ εἴρηχαν καὶ εἰ μὴ, 

    <lb n="14"/>ὅτι ὁ υἱός μου <choice><reg>ἀσθενεῖ</reg><orig>ἀσθενῖ</orig></choice> <choice><reg>δεινῶς</reg><orig>δινῶς</orig></choice> τού<unclear>του</unclear> 

    <lb n="15"/><choice><reg>ἕνεκα</reg><orig>εἵνεκα</orig></choice> ἀνηρχόμην. ἐὰν δὲ θέλῃς 

    <lb n="16"/><unclear>ἃς</unclear> <choice><reg>ἔχω</reg><orig><unclear>ἔ</unclear>χωι</orig></choice> παρὰ Θαυμαστῆι σὺν ὧι 

    <lb n="17"/>ἦρκ<unclear>α</unclear>ς ἡμέρα<unclear>ς</unclear> τὰ <unclear>β</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/><unclear>β</unclear>αρο<unclear>λι</unclear> 

    <lb n="18"/>καν<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ελωστης δύνηται τ<unclear>α</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="19"/>πλήρωσιν τῶν <expan><ex>δραχμῶν</ex></expan> <num value="100">ρ</num> καὶ τοῦ φιλαν

    <lb n="20" break="no"/>θρώπου <choice><reg>ἑτοιμάσαι</reg><orig>ἑ<unclear>τ</unclear>υμάσαι</orig></choice> <supplied reason="lost">π</supplied>έμψω σοι 

    <lb n="21"/>ἐὰν <choice><reg>μὴ</reg><orig>μὴι</orig></choice> <choice><reg>πάλιν</reg><orig>πάλειν</orig></choice> εἰς <unclear>τὸ</unclear> <unclear>σ</unclear>αριν ἔ<unclear>λθ</unclear>ω 

    <lb n="22"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="line"/> </ab></div>
